<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-175] Plugin cache should be reset when addPackages is called</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-175</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If there are packages defined on the configuration, but the &apos;element type&apos; plugin cache has already been built, plugins for the new package are never found.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have a fix and I&apos;ll commit shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12636957">LOG4J2-175</key>
            <summary>Plugin cache should be reset when addPackages is called</summary>
